Once the data is downloaded and unzipped there are 2 folders - test and train and following files
  - features_info.txt: Shows information about the variables used on the feature vector.
  - features.txt': List of all features.
  - activity_labels.txt': Links the class labels with their activity name.
  - Test folder has
      - Inertial Signals: Not used in this project
      -	test/X_test.txt: Test set.
      -	test/y_test.txt': Test labels.
  - Train folder has
      - Inertial Signals: Not used in this project
      -	train/X_train.txt': Training set.
      -	train/y_train.txt': Training labels.
  
  - Variables used in the R Script (run_analysis.R) :
  	x_train	- Features for training data set
	y_train - Activity id in training data set
	sub_train - Subject id in training data set

	x_test	- Features for testing data set
	y_train - Activity id in testing data set
	sub_train - Subject id in testing data set

	train_merge - dataset for trainig data including Acitivity id, Subject id and all features
	test_merge - dataset for test group data including Acitivity id, Subject id and all features
	Allmerge  - combination of above two.
	
	meanNstd_df - dataset from Allmerge with mean and std values.
	Tidy_df    - Fianl tidy data set.	
